cff-version: 1.2.0
message: "If you use QuantMill in your research, please cite it as below."
title: "QuantMill: an honest full-chain open-source AI quant platform"
abstract: >-
  QuantMill is an open-source full-chain AI quant platform for HK/US/A-share
  markets, whose defining feature is honesty: it runs built-in credibility
  checks (Deflated Sharpe Ratio, Probability of Backtest Overfitting),
  cross-sectional selection, cross-market validation, and forward/survivorship
  bias quantification to falsify its own backtests instead of overselling them.
type: software
authors:
